{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Screen.height","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/height","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availHeight\"><code>availHeight</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availLeft\"><code>availLeft</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availTop\"><code>availTop</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availWidth\"><code>availWidth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/colorDepth\"><code>colorDepth</code></a></li><li><em><code>height</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/left\"><code>left</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozBrightness\"><code>mozBrightness</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozEnabled\"><code>mozEnabled</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\"><code>orientation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/pixelDepth\"><code>pixelDepth</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientationchange_event\"><code>Screen: orientationchange event</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/top\"><code>top</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/lockOrientation\"><code>lockOrientation()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/unlockOrientation\"><code>unlockOrientation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>CSSOM に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>Screen.height</strong></code> は読み取り専用プロパティで、画面の高さをピクセル数で返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <var>height</var> = window.screen.height</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js; notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>availHeight <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>height<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token comment\">// Something is occupying some screen real estate!</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このプロパティによって与えられる高さのすべてがウィンドウに利用できるわけではないことに注意してください。タスクバーなどのウィジェットや、 OS と統合された他の特殊なアプリケーションウィンドウ (例えば、ウィンドウの上で追加のツールバーのように動作するように最小化された Spinner プレイヤーなど) は、ブラウザーウィンドウや他のアプリケーションに利用可能な空間の量を減らすことがあります。</p>\n\n<p>Internet Explorer は、画面の高さを報告する際に拡大率の設定を考慮します。拡大率が 100% に設定されている場合のみ、実際の画面の高さを返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-screen-height\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"ja\">Screen.height の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Screen.height","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/height/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"注","id":"notes"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"Screen.height は読み取り専用プロパティで、画面の高さをピクセル数で返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Screen.height","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Screen.height","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{